This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image analysis and segmentation. Additionally, the use of deep learning techniques for segmentation suggests that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper may also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves the extraction of specific features from images. Finally, the use of image analysis techniques for medical applications suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
